PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of NOVA SCOTIA of the administration and control over three parcels of waterfront land situate at Caribou Harbour, in Pictou County, that contain a total area of some 6.82 acres (2.76 hectares), which are to be used for marine purposes, including the improvement of the Caribou Ferry Terminal.
